<main>
	<!-- ABOUT -->
	<section class="section-about">
		<div class="about">

			<div class="about-heading sr-default">
				<h1 id="about" class="heading-secondary">You need a strategy</h1>
				<h2 class="about-heading--sub"><em>My work is guaranteed to grow your business</em></h2>
			</div>

			<div class="section-who">
				<div class="who sr-default">
					<div class="who__text">
						<h3 class="heading-tertiary-blue who__heading">Who Am I</h3>
						<p class="who__sub">My name is Dan and I currently work from home doing web development, design, and digital marketing for different businesses. I also have a side job where I work with designers everyday preparing their work for print and ensuring they get the right product. I'm also a fan of the color black and blue if you couldn't tell.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="who__border"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="mission sr-default">
					<div class="mission__border"></div>
					<div class="mission__text">
						<h3 class="heading-tertiary-blue">My mission</h3>
						<p class="who__sub">I am not and do not ever plan on being the average freelancer charging low prices for even lower quality work. My work is guarenteed and at the end of the day I am doing something I love for a client that I believe can grow exponentially. Let me be the catalyst to your growth.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h1 class="about-heading heading-secondary sr-default">What to expect</h1>
			<div class="about-box sr-about-box">
				<svg class="about-box__icon" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
					<title>compass</title>
