				</svg>
				<h3 class="heading-tertiary-dark">Intuitive</h3>
				<p class="about-box__text">
					I have an affinity towards doing things right. Custom designs help make my work intuitive to your client.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="about-box sr-about-box">
				<svg class="about-box__icon" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
					<title>laptop</title>
