				<p class="about-box__text">
					From SEO to social media, my work is conversion centered and will guarantee you more leads.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
		<div class="about-why sr-default">
			<h3 class="heading-tertiary-blue">Why choose me?</h3>
			<div class="about-why__text">
				<p class="about-why__main"><em>I understand what your business needs in order to grow.</em></p>
				<p class="about-why__sub">A stunning and user friendly website, active social media accounts with the right content, and every aspect of SEO covered.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="about-why__border"></div>
		</div>

	</section>
	<!-- /ABOUT -->

	<!-- SERVICES -->
	<section class="section-services parallax--services">
		<h2 id="services" class="heading-secondary-blue section-services__heading sr-default">Services</h2>
			<div class="services">
				<div class="services__box sr-services-box">
					<h3 class="heading-tertiary-light">Web development</h3>
					<ul class="services__list">
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Custom coded</span> Website creation using modern technologies. Perfect for those who want a website done right tailored to their business.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Wordpress</span> Website that gives you the ability to edit content as you please. Great for some businesses, others not so much.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--price">One time charge + yearly hosting</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="services__box sr-services-box">
					<h3 class="heading-tertiary-light">Graphic Design</h3>
					<ul class="services__list">
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Social media</span> Posts designed for user engagement. A necessity for any business.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Media</span> Print and digital - advertisements, business cards, etc. Get your business out there.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Branding</span> Logo design and other assets to make your brand timeless.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--price">One time charge or included in marketing package</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="services__box sr-services-box">
					<h3 class="heading-tertiary-light">Digital Marketing</h3>
					<ul class="services__list">
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">SEO</span> Google analytics + adwords, Google maps submission, XML sitemap, SSL, site speed, and much more to get to the top of Google.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--option">Digital media</span> Personalized designs for your business. Includes social media, print and digital design, and branding.</li>
						<li class="services__list-item"><span class="services__list-item--price">Monthly package + Site updates &amp; graphic design</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		<p class="services__contact">For pricing and guidance on your best option</p>
		<a href="#contact" class="services__link">
			<div class="services__btn">
					Contact Me
			</div>
		</a>
	</section>
	<!-- /SERVICES -->

	<!-- OTHER -->
	<section class="section-other">
		<div class="choose-me">
			<div class="choose-me__box sr-default">
				<h1 class="heading-tertiary-blue choose-me__heading">Why me over sites like Wix and Squarespace?</h1>
				<p class="choose-me__text">What happens when you need to fine tune a theme or something goes wrong? Making it responsive? You will probably hire a developer down the road because of these problems.</p>
				<p class="choose-me__text">Wordpress is similar to this, but having someone that has already tried and failed can streamline the process and let you focus on running the business you love.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="choose-me__border--2"></div>
			<div class="choose-me__box sr-default">
				<h1 class="heading-tertiary-blue choose-me__heading">Why should you have a dedicated designer &amp; developer?</h1>
				<p class="choose-me__text">Having a go to person for all of your digital needs can be very useful and efficient. Need a new section added to your website? Maybe a new business card or food menu design? I'm a call or email away.</p>
				<p class="choose-me__text">Many of us in life have learned that communication is key, it is my main priority. I <span class="choose-me__text--em">want</span> to address issues in order for the product to be perfect.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section-other__spots sr-default">
			<h2 class="heading-tertiary-blue">Spots are running low</h2>
			<div class="about-why__text">
				<p class="about-why__main"><em>Grab your spot to grow your business</em></p>
				<p class="about-why__sub">I currently have availability for <span class="choose-me__text--em">one</span> custom coded website at a time. I am taking on multiple Wordpress, graphic design, and marketing package clients.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="about-why__border"></div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<!-- /OTHER -->

	<!-- CONTACT -->
	<section class="section-contact">
		<div class="contact">
			<h2 id="contact" class="heading-secondary-blue">Contact Me</h2>
			<div class="contact__form">
				<form id="contact-form" action="/" method="POST" class="form">
					<div class="form__group">
						<input type="text" class="form__input" placeholder="Full Name" id="name" name="name" required>
						<label for="name" class="form__label">Full Name</label>
					</div>
					<div class="form__group">
						<input type="email" class="form__input" placeholder="Email" id="email" name="email" required>
						<label for="email" class="form__label">Email</label>
					</div>

					<div class="form__heading">
						<h3 class="heading-tertiary-light">Receive pricing for</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="form__group form__check-flex">
						<div class="form__check-group">
							<input type="checkbox" class="form__check-input" id="website" name="website">
							<label for="website" class="form__check-label">
								<span class="form__check-button"></span>
								Web Development
							</label>
						</div>
						<div class="form__check-group">
							<input type="checkbox" class="form__check-input" id="design" name="design">
							<label for="design" class="form__check-label">
								<span class="form__check-button"></span>
								Graphic Design
							</label>
						</div>

						<div class="form__check-group">
							<input type="checkbox" class="form__check-input" id="marketing" name="marketing">
							<label for="marketing" class="form__check-label">
								<span class="form__check-button"></span>
								Marketing Package
							</label>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="form__group">
						<textarea name="message" id="message" class="form__message" placeholder="Company info / requested work / concerns..."></textarea>
					</div>

					<div class="form__group form__submit">
						<button type="submit" class="form__button">Send</button>
					</div>
					<div class="alert">Message has been sent</div>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<!-- /CONTACT -->
</main>

